==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Disillusion
<hw>Dis`il*lu"sion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or
process of freeing from an illusion, or the state of being freed
therefrom.</def> <rj><au>Lowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disillusion</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Disillusion
<hw>Dis`il*lu"sion</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To free from an illusion;
to disillusionize.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>disillusioning</ent>⟦br⟧
